Safety and activity of RRx-001 in patients with advanced cancer: a 
first-in-human, open-label, dose-escalation phase 1 study.

Reid T(1), Oronsky B(2), Scicinski J(2), Scribner CL(3), Knox SJ(4), Ning S(4), 
