[Effects of DNA quality on the measurement of telomere length].

[Article in Russian]

Voropaeva EN(1)(2), Maksimov VN(1), Malyutina SK(1), Bobak M(3), Voevoda MI(1).

Author information:
(1)Institute of Internal and Preventive Medicine, Siberian Branch, Russian 
Academy of Medical Sciences, Novosibirsk, 630089 Russia.
(2)vena.81@mail.ru.
